<sect1 id="learning.lucene.index-opening">
    <title>Index opening and creation</title>

    <para>
        All index operations (creating new index, adding document to the index, deleting document, 
        searching through the index) need index object. It can be obtained using two methods:
    </para>

    <example id="learning.lucene.index-opening.creation">
        <title>Lucene index creation</title>
        
        <programlisting language="php"><![CDATA[
$index = Zend_Search_Lucene::create($indexPath);
]]></programlisting>
    </example>
    
    <para>
        or:
    </para>

    <example id="learning.lucene.index-opening.creation">
        <title>Lucene index opening</title>
        
        <programlisting language="php"><![CDATA[
$index = Zend_Search_Lucene::open($indexPath);
]]></programlisting>
    </example>
</sect1>
